==English==

=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]]: /ˌweɪ'leɪ/

===Verb===
'''to waylay''' ([[waylaid]], [[waylaid]])

# To lie in wait for and attack from [[ambush]]
# To [[accost]] or [[intercept]] unexpectedly
# To wait in hiding to attack;
# To wait for and then stop someone with the aim of attacking, or to talk to them

